OVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Lockdowns">2.3Lockdowns</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#First_wave:_Nation-wide">2.3.1First wave: Nation-wide</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Second_wave:_State-wide_and_localised">2.3.2Second wave: State-wide and localised</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Administration,_committees_and_task_forces">2.4Administration, committees and task forces</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Military">2.5Military</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Private_sector">2.6Private sector</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#International">2.7International</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#International_support">2.7.1International support</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Response_shortages_and_criticism">2.8Response shortages and criticism</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Evacuations_by_India_related_to_the_COVID-19_pandemic">3Evacuations by India related to the COVID-19 pandemic</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Background">3.1Background</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#COVID-19_pandemic">3.1.1COVID-19 pandemic</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Migration">3.1.2Migration</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Previous_evacuations">3.1.3Previous evacuations</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#International_2">3.2International</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#January%E2%80%93April_2020">3.2.1January–April 2020</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#May_2020%E2%80%93present:_Vande_Bharat_Mission">3.2.2May 2020–present: Vande Bharat Mission</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_I">3.2.3Phase I</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_II">3.2.4Phase II</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_III">3.2.5Phase III</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_IV">3.2.6Phase IV</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_V">3.2.7Phase V</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_VI">3.2.8Phase VI</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_VII">3.2.9Phase VII</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Samudra_Setu_II">3.2.10Samudra Setu II</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Domestic">3.3Domestic</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Reception">3.4Reception</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Incidents">3.5Incidents</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Air_India_Express_Flight_1344">3.5.1Air India Express Flight 1344</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Air_India_Flight_AI-312_27-Aug_Fiasco">3.5.2Air India Flight AI-312 27-Aug Fiasco</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Impact">4Impact</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Displacement_of_migrant_workers">4.1Displacement of migrant workers</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Drug_shortages">4.