0">3.2.1January–April 2020</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#May_2020%E2%80%93present:_Vande_Bharat_Mission">3.2.2May 2020–present: Vande Bharat Mission</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_I">3.2.3Phase I</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_II">3.2.4Phase II</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_III">3.2.5Phase III</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_IV">3.2.6Phase IV</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_V">3.2.7Phase V</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_VI">3.2.8Phase VI</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Phase_VII">3.2.9Phase VII</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Samudra_Setu_II">3.2.10Samudra Setu II</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Domestic">3.3Domestic</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Reception">3.4Reception</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Incidents">3.5Incidents</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Air_India_Express_Flight_1344">3.5.1Air India Express Flight 1344</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Air_India_Flight_AI-312_27-Aug_Fiasco">3.5.2Air India Flight AI-312 27-Aug Fiasco</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Impact">4Impact</a><ul><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Displacement_of_migrant_workers">4.1Displacement of migrant workers</a></li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/COVID-19_pandemic_in_India#Drug_shortages">4.